  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hilltop Schools operates a girls Academy to ensure girls attend school and become leaders in their community. The Academy has a holistic approach, providing 280 girls quality education, healthcare, nutrition, and psychosocial support. School for our students is entirely free. Your donation goes towards learning materials, social work programs, extracurricular activities, leadership training, daily meals, and retrofitting classrooms to fit COVID-19 safety and distancing protocols.</narrative>
